'''埃姆赫斯特'''（Elmhurst），當地亦漢譯為'''艾滸'''，是[[美國|美國]][[纽约市|纽约市]][[皇后区|皇后区]]的一个[[工人阶级|工人阶级]]兼[[中产阶级|中产阶级]]社区，北到罗斯福大道，南到[[长岛高速公路|长岛高速公路]]，东到交界大道（Junction Boulevard），西到纽约联络铁路。<ref name=nytimes-elmhurst>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1985/08/04/realestate/if-you-re-thinking-of-living-in-elmhurst.html |title=If You're Thinking of Living in: Elmhurst |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |first=Amanda |last=Marques |date=1985-08-04 |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-date=2016-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812185002/http://www.nytimes.com/1985/08/04/realestate/if-you-re-thinking-of-living-in-elmhurst.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==历史==
村庄由荷兰人建于1652年，名为Middenburgh，是[[新尼德兰|新尼德兰]]城市[[新阿姆斯特丹|新阿姆斯特丹]]的郊区。早期的居民来自附近的Maspat，因受到当地美洲土着人的威胁和攻击而迁来此处<ref name=nytimes-elmhurst/><ref name="SeyfriedAsadorian2012">{{cite book|author1=Vincent F. Seyfried|author2=William Asadorian|title=Old Queens, N.Y., in Early Photographs: 261 Prints|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qUHCAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA23|date=2012-08-28|publisher=Courier Corporation|isbn=978-0-486-13601-1|pages=23–|access-date=2017-01-20|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715233858/https://books.google.com/books?id=qUHCAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当英国在1664年接管新尼德兰时，将其更名为新城（New Town）。1683年，皇后县分设五镇时，新城村为新城镇的驻地<ref name=nytimes-elmhurst/>，设有市政厅，监狱，税务局和牧师办公室，是该镇的中心，村庄位于现在森林公园以北，和法拉盛草地以西。<ref name="SeyfriedAsadorian2012"/>

1854年，马车线路大街线开通，1876年[[长岛铁路|长岛铁路]]通车，都吸引许多居民来到这个社区<ref name="SeyfriedAsadorian2012"/>。1897年，该镇改为现名，意为榆树丛。<ref name="SeyfriedAsadorian2012"/><ref name=nytimes-elmhurst/>1896年至1910年期间，埃姆赫斯特发展成为一个时尚的住宅区。1936年，[[独立地铁系统|独立地铁系统]]的皇后大道线通车，刺激该社区的经济发展，但也破坏了许多老建筑。<ref name=nytimes-elmhurst/><ref name="SeyfriedAsadorian2012"/>

在第二次世界大战之前，埃姆赫斯特几乎完全是[[犹太人|犹太人]]和[[意大利人|意大利人]]的社区。战后，埃姆赫斯特发展成为纽约市最具种族多样性的社区之一<ref>{{cite news|author=Kleinman, Dena|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&res=9503E4DE163BF935A35753C1A964948260|title=A Hospital Where Ethnic Change is Constant|newspaper=The New York Times|date=October 6, 1982|accessdate=2012-09-18|quote=Dr. Stanley Bleich had been an intern less than a month at the municipal hospital in Elmhurst, Queens,... one of the city's 16 municipal hospitals, [which] is in what immigration officials have described as the city's most ethnically diverse neighborhood.|archive-date=2007-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071211092855/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&res=9503E4DE163BF935A35753C1A964948260|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到1980年代，居住在该社区的有来自112个国家的居民。其中最大的种族群体是拉美裔和[[华人|华人]]<ref name="cny 201502">{{cite web | url=http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20150209/REAL_ESTATE/302089995/housing-gains-in-elmhurst-queens-leave-many-cold | title=Housing gains in Elmhurst, Queens, leave many cold | publisher=Crain's New York | date=2015-02-09 | accessdate=2015-06-08 | author=Kerry Murtha | archive-date=2017-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328175454/http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20150209/REAL_ESTATE/302089995/housing-gains-in-elmhurst-queens-leave-many-cold | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==人口==
根据从2010年美国人口普查，埃姆赫斯特的人口为88427人，比2000年增长了0.5％。该社区面积{{convert|750.28|acres}}，人口密度为{{convert|117.9|PD/acre|PD/sqmi PD/sqkm}}<ref name=PLP5>[http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/planning/download/pdf/data-maps/nyc-population/census2010/t_pl_p5_nta.pdf Table PL-P5 NTA: Total Population and Persons Per Acre - New York City Neighborhood Tabulation Areas*, 2010] {{Wayback|url=http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/planning/download/pdf/data-maps/nyc-population/census2010/t_pl_p5_nta.pdf |date=20160610175331 }}, Population Division - [[New_York_City|New York City]] Department of City Planning, 2012年2月. Accessed 2016-06-16</ref>。

该社区的种族构成是白人占6.6%，非洲裔占1.3%，美洲土著占0.2%，亚裔占43.8%。拉美裔占人口的46.1％。<ref name=PLP3A>[http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/planning/download/pdf/data-maps/nyc-population/census2010/t_pl_p3a_nta.pdf Table PL-P3A NTA: Total Population by Mutually Exclusive Race and Hispanic Origin - New York City Neighborhood Tabulation Areas*, 2010] {{Wayback|url=http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/planning/download/pdf/data-maps/nyc-population/census2010/t_pl_p3a_nta.pdf |date=20160610170733 }}, Population Division - [[New_York_City|New York City]] Department of City Planning, 2011-03-29. Accessed 2016-06-14</ref>

埃姆赫斯特快速成长的唐人街是皇后区的第二个[[唐人街|唐人街]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://queens.about.com/od/photogalleries/ig/Photos-of-Elmhurst/Elmhurst-Chinatown-.htm |title=A Growing Chinatown in Elmhurst |accessdate=2010-10-01 |archive-date=2014-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711032947/http://queens.about.com/od/photogalleries/ig/Photos-of-Elmhurst/Elmhurst-Chinatown-.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是皇后区的第二大唐人街，仅次于[[法拉盛|法拉盛]]唐人街。它最初只是局限在81街和康沃尔大道之间的百老汇，现在已经扩展到45大道和惠特尼大道，发展成为[[法拉盛|法拉盛]]唐人街的卫星城。

